1B Checks have been added & can be deposited & withdrawn from the coin pouch. 5+ mini-games including; Duel arena, barrows, pest control, & graveyard arena. IPB Forums w/ custom user bars, integration system as well as a custom skin. Social media pages; Twitter, Facebook, & Youtube. 5+ bosses, including 100% Nex with stages etc. Full bank system with searching, tabs, etc. All skills working even construction. 100% Clan chat system with ranks. Stats go up to 100 instead of 99. Over powered weapons & armor. All known bugs have been fixed. Unique mystery box system. Great donator benefits. Custom point system. 65+ achievements. Custom Homepage. 180+ custom items. HD textures & fog. DDOS Protection. Flawless skilling. Good economy. Working flasks. Custom shops. Custom NPCS. Daily Updates. Flower Poker Full Screen. Duo slayer. Good PVP. 24/7 VPS. Quests. Dicing.

item.description:
@Ix_Soulcist_xI wrote:

You have a rather nice-made theme but it’s also a little buggy, do like the color scheme though. As far as the video, I don’t personally take much time to watch videos and rather see pictures as it’s faster and quicker most of the time to see if I like the server or not. I would recommend adding those and a video for those who do enjoy watching them. From what I did watch from the video, I have to admit that the song is a little annoying.

Good luck with the server though.
